Introduction

Woni is a South Korean singer and rapper under THE MUZE Entertainment. She is best known as the leader, lead rapper and sub vocalist of the girl group RESCENE.

She debuted as a member of RESCENE on March 26, 2024, with their single album "Re:Scene".
